<%= render partial: "layouts/nav" %>

<div class="about-top">
  <div class="about-us-text">
    <div class="about-header-content">
      We all love events!
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="about">
  <div class="about-stats row group">
    <div class="col s12 m8 l10 no-margin">
      <div class="about-content">
        <h4 class="teal_text">You have the idea...</h4>
        What do you do when you have an event and all the event management applications available are too heavy but with little functionality to serve your purpose?
        How do you organize a small get-together with your friends, without having to go through a rigorous event creation process and without bothering about all the complexities of event management?
        <h4 class="teal_text">We Make It Happen</h4>
        Our team of world-class developers is ready to help you bring your passions to life. There are tons of possibilities we believe can be achieved without sweat.
        Oh, and we are not just developers, we love events too! We have a lot of experience in planning events and know exactly what you want.
        Wouldn't you like to take this journey with us?
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col s12 m4 l2 no-padding stat-group">
      <div class="col s12 m12 l12 no-margin">
        <div class="milestones">
          <div class="orange_text stats-large"><%= @presenter.event_count %> </div>
          <p class="card-title"><%= "Event".pluralize(@presenter.event_count)%></p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col s12 m12 l12 no-margin">
        <div class="milestones">
          <div class="orange_text stats-large"><%= @presenter.ticket_count %> </div>
          <p class="card-title"><%= "Ticket".pluralize(@presenter.ticket_count)%> Sold</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col s12 m12 l12 no-margin">
        <div class="milestones">
          <div class="orange_text stats-large"><%= @presenter.manager_count %> </div>
          <p class="card-title"><%= "Event Manager".pluralize(@presenter.manager_count)%></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row card-group">
    <div class="col s12 m4 l4">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-image">
          <img src="https://pixabay.com/static/uploads/photo/2016/06/20/20/20/table-1469719__340.jpg">
          <div class="feature-details">
            <div class="feature-title">
              Who We Are
            </div>
            <div class="feature-content">
              <p>We are a group of fun-loving people who love events! Our team of party-goers know how important events are to you.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col s12 m4 l4">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-image">
          <img src="https://pixabay.com/static/uploads/photo/2016/07/21/09/04/apple-1532055__340.jpg">
          <div class="feature-details">
            <div class="feature-title">
              Why Choose Us?
            </div>
            <div class="feature-content">
              <p>We use innovative tools to make sure you create memorable experiences for yourself and your friends.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col s12 m4 l4">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-image">
          <img src="https://pixabay.com/static/uploads/photo/2014/04/02/17/03/freedom-307791__180.png">
          <div class="feature-details">
            <div class="feature-title">
              Our Community
            </div>
            <div class="feature-content">
              <p>You can be part of the great work we do just by joining our community of fun-loving people. They love to help...</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
